{"tid":2018022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突然有幾條問題想問下攬炒巴","createTime":"2020-05-15T11:18:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T11:47:17.000Z","uid":53566,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bfc24bbb6c0fa203d5cd000eb7bc7d2b2261e8b7","tid":2018022,"uid":53566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:18:10.000Z","msg":"１。有隻黑警警眷指責你不盡力攬炒，反而係幫泛民助選，有無諗住再寫文講解？<br />\n２。見到連登以外有d人話你販賣希望，咁你有咩見解？<br />\n３。上下議院係好主意，但係好少講後續行動，同時有無機會被正苦話係非法組織，而飛去海外開會？<br />\n４。以今日嘅正苦連環拳，完全係打擊士氣，始終抗爭者需要一個苦海明燈去防止迷失，你地有無行動去重振旗鼓同埋應對正苦攻勢？<br />\n５。sister city個壇野，有d講得太虛無，海外組織係未進行緊溝通？同本地一様，海外戰線都需要利好消息，士氣太差啦"},{"pid":"ee54998cfdcc17190be6372c834a7a6b98d0ebac","tid":2018022,"uid":53566,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:26:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01c891269daacfea78327c3e577c3e8992d4061","tid":2018022,"uid":53566,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:30:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dde469a071afcf00221fd2f7e6cdcd32d675d175","tid":2018022,"uid":53566,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:47:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}